    {
      "id": "t33",
      "type": "text",
      "context": "div.layout6_content-left > div.margin-bottom > p.text-size-medium",
      "en": "Oleochemicals, derived from natural oils and fats including palm, coconut and animal sources, provide an alternative to petroleum-based products."
    },
    {
      "id": "t34",
      "type": "text",
      "context": "div.layout6_content-left > div.margin-bottom > p.text-size-medium",
      "en": "These compounds serve as key ingredients in soaps, detergents, cosmetics, pharmaceuticals and various industrial applications. Responsibly sourced oleochemicals represent a sustainable substitute for conventional petrochemicals."
    },
    {
      "id": "t35",
      "type": "text",
      "context": "div.layout6_text-wrapper > div.margin-bottom > h3.heading-style-h6",
